<figureCitation box="[542,632,1425,1451]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="4.[189,232,1894,1920]" captionTargetBox="[300,1304,283,1834]" captionTargetId="figure@4.[264,1324,265,1858]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="Fig. 1. A–C, G–H. Canthon (G.) smaragdulus smaragdulus (Fabricius, 1781). – D–F, I–J. Canthon (G.) fulgidus fulgidus Redtenbacher, 1868. A, D. Ventral surface of meso- and metafemora. B, E. Metasternal anterior lobe convex. C, F. Dorsal view showing convex pygidium. G, I. Paramera lateral view. H, J. Paramera dorsal view. Scale bar: 2.0 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3787889" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3787889/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="4">Fig. 1B</figureCitation>
