<figureCitation box="[1234,1305,1425,1451]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="7.[189,232,1930,1956]" captionTargetBox="[201,1366,761,1893]" captionTargetId="figure@7.[197,1391,751,1893]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="Fig. 2. A. Canthon (G.) smaragdulus smaragdulus (Fabricius, 1781). – B–D. C. (G.) smaragdulus subviridis Schmidt, 1922 stat. rev. A–B. Habitus. C. Male protibial spur. D. Female protibial spur. Scale bar: A–B = 5.0 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3787891" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3787891/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="4">Fig. 2</figureCitation>
